<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَخْبَرَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٤٤٢٩ -<span class="c5"> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا مَعْمَرٌ، عَنِ ابْنِ شُبْرُمَةَ،<span class="c5"> أَنَّهُ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«فِي الْمَاءِ الشُفْعَةُ»</span>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ مَعْمَرٌ:</span> <span class="c2">«فَلَمْ يُعْجِبْنِي مَا قَالَ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>